    dc:date "2015" ;
    dc:title "Two new species of the millipede family Blaniulidae (Diplopoda, Julida) from caves in central and southeastern Europe" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.235352>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.235351>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.235353>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.235362> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.235352>
    dc:description "FIGURES 5 – 9. Cibiniulus slovacus sp. n., paratype male. 5. posterior gonopod, lateral view; 6. apical half of posterior gonopod, lateral view; 7. posterior gonopod, mesal view; 8. left first leg, posterior view; 9. apical part of right first leg, anterior view. a: apophyses / modified setae, s: sternum, cl: claw, dl: dorsal lobe, fs: femoral striations, ll: leaf-shaped lamella, sh: setiferous hump, st: striations on leaf-shaped lamella, ta: tarsus, ti: tibia, tr: triangular area, vl: ventral lobe. Scale lines: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/235352/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.235351>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 4. Cibiniulus slovacus sp. n., paratype male. 1. anterior gonopods, posterior view; 2. anterior gonopods, posterolateral view; 3. anterior gonopods, lateral view; 4. second pair of legs with penis, posterior view. – f: postero-mesal flange, p: penis, t: telopodite, cp: coxal processes, ls: lanceolate seta. Scale lines: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/235351/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.235353>
    dc:description "FIGURES 10 – 12. Cibiniulus slovacus sp. n., 10. holotype male posterior gonopods, lateral and mesal view; 11. holotype male posterior gonopods apex, lateral and mesal view; 12. female vulva, posterior view. s: sternum, dl: dorsal lobe, ll: leaf-shaped lamella, rs: receptaculum seminis, st: striations on leaf-shaped lamella, vl: ventral lobe." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/235353/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.235362>
    dc:description "FIGURE 43. Distribution of the genera Cibiniulus Verhoeff, 1897 and Thassoblaniulus Mauriès, 1985." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/235362/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

